Package ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure.drosophila.wingpouch

Implements methods and objects to generate and describe structure models of Drosophila wing pouches.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InteractiveStructure
    Allows the user to interact with the detected wing pouch.
    PreProcessing
    Pre-processing of the Wg-Ptc-AB maximum intensity projection.
    WDiscCenterDetection
    Computes the center of the wing disc (required for the inference of the wing orientation).
    WPouchBoundariesDetection
    Detects the trajectory of each of the four half-boundaries forming the A/P and D/V boundaries.
    WPouchCenterDetection
    Identifies the center of the wing pouch from the skeleton of the wing pouch structure
    WPouchCompartmentsDetection
    Detects the four compartments DA, DP, VA, and VP using snakes.
    WPouchContourDetection
    Detects the contour of the wing pouch.
    WPouchOrientationDetection
    Identifies the orientation of the wing (A/P and D/V directions).
    WPouchOverlay
    Adds information on top of the preview of the wing pouch structure.
    WPouchStructure
    This class describes the structure of the Drosophila wing pouch.
    WPouchStructureDataset
    Implements methods to save wing structure datasets.
    WPouchStructureDetector
    Identifies the wing pouch contour, compartments, and A/P and D/V boundaries from Wg-Ptc-AB confocal images.
    WPouchStructureMeasurements
    Contains the measurements taken from the structure model of the wing pouch.
    WPouchStructureMeasurementsParser
    Implements methods to write the measurements taken from the structure model of the wing pouch to files.
    WPouchStructureParser
    XML parser for importing and exporting WPouchStructure objects.
    WPouchStructureSnake
    Describes a structure as a snake/B-splines.
    WPouchSystem
    Drosophila wing pouch system.

Package ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure.drosophila.wingpouch Description

Implements methods and objects to generate and describe structure models of Drosophila wing pouches.
